            . I live near Spencer. On Tuesday evening about seven o'clock I saw the prisoner pass his window; pushing a pair of shoes under his coat; I went and told him he had a pair of shoes; he made no answer, but walked on - I went and told Spencer Dickenson followed him.</p>
